{"tid":647886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[進步、無私與團結的執政集團]「要讓人民用網路監督中國政府...」 李克強談話遭刪","createTime":"2018-04-30T08:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T10:49:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2d88f8dcd204e3e844bdefc21167d31630884e","tid":647886,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"中國因為是極權國家，對網路、電視等媒體都有嚴格控制。中國國務院總理李克強之前曾在談話中表示，要讓中國人民用網路監督政府行為，不過其談話現在已從中國網路上消失。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，李克強上周五在中國國務院第一次廉政工作會議談到政府作為，他認為政府要推進政務公開，並讓人民透過互聯網、大數據等資料來全程監督政府的行為。他也希望政府權力能在陽光下運作，有效治理不作為與亂作為，讓腐敗能無處遁形。<br />\n<br />\n不過李克強的這段談話內容很快就從中國國務院官網上消失，現在中國政府官方網站上已看不到「互聯網」、「全程監督政府行為」等字眼。李克強的話也變成「以強化對權力運行制約和監督為重點，大力推進廉潔政府建設。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2411076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2411076&d=c0IW%2Fu7PGTltYwpW2bMHqpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=5ebb8485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2411076&h=2af4eb8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2411076</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520a524761188cb58741a97943bba155de562da3","tid":647886,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"習總  ：強仔你講乜撚野，即刻同我ban左佢"},{"pid":"ce2ff976c861ff6f57b51a8b99b8bc23a5f6d1f2","tid":647886,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"In 贏國 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea536ddc04650334eafd6d6add27764d05d5a936","tid":647886,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"阿強都贏"},{"pid":"008be7bacf764e6dce6c30b210e139d60e196add","tid":647886,"uid":70309,